-- Philippines' Rizal Bank in talks to sell 20 pct stake to Cathay Financial
-- By Karen Lema and Neil Jerome Morales
-- Thu Aug 28, 2014 11:43PM EDT
-- None



MANILA, Aug 29 (Reuters) - The Philippines' Rizal Commercial Banking Corp <RCB.PS> is in talks to sell a 20 percent stake to Taiwan's Cathay Financial Holding Co <2882.TW>, Rizal Bank's chief executive said on Friday.

Rizal Bank may sell a 10 percent stake while shareholder CVC Capital Partners Ltd may also sell 10 percent, CEO Lorenzo Tan told reporters.